<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#000000">1. Cấu tr&uacute;c v&ograve;ng lặp while</span></span></h2>

<p><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>C&uacute; ph&aacute;p:</strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<p><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#000000">1</span></span></p>

